I had them sort of fanned
out in different ways.

00:41:32.090 --> 00:41:35.040
I had them,
a kind of strange rotating option.

00:41:35.040 --> 00:41:37.090
I had them angled at a different way.

00:41:37.100 --> 00:41:40.660
I had all these options and I walked
into Randy's office and I said,

00:41:40.740 --> 00:41:44.700
"Okay, well I have a couple solutions for
you for this problem of showing

00:41:44.700 --> 00:41:45.790
brushes when you're in portrait.

